 kind of objectives are set. If the objective is to beat the market or maximize potential returns irrespective of underlying probability for permanently losing capital, then most</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745276-interested-in-retirement-income-this-is-why-schd-should-be-your-core-step", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:15:00"}, {"id": "4745320", "title": "Tesla: Get Out At The Top (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"One red umbrella at center of multiple black umbrellas\" data-id=\"167532036\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> <