providing an exceptional return for investors. Given the stock has exhibited relatively muted increases in EBITDA over last year\u2019s trough, some</span></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745316-united-natural-foods-why-is-it-going-up", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:51:04"}, {"id": "4745314", "title": "Sustainability And The Investment Case: Heavy Industry", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of country road under construction\" data-id=\"1316313214\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SimonSkafar/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>By Benedict Buckley, CFA, Dimitry Dayen, CFA, Adam Meyers</p> <p>Thinking of sustainability and the fundamental investment process together makes sense, as sustainability factors should reinforce a strong fundamental case for owning equity securities, either as a source</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745314-sustainability-and-the-investment-case-heavy-industry", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:46:16"}, {"id": "4745326", "title": "Rolls-Royce: Service Margin Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rolls Royce Merlin aero engine\" data-id=\"492400245\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy_Oxley</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I initially covered Rolls-Royce Holdings plc (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RYCEY\" title=\"Rolls-Royce Holdings plc\">OTCPK:RYCEY</a>) in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4700975-rolls-royce-room-for-earnings-upgrades\">June of this year</a> with a positive view on their turnaround, which has continued with the company delivering on guidance and re-instating dividends as well as reducing debt. I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745326-rolls-royce-service-margin-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:40:00"}, {"id": "4745309", "title": "CHIQ: Beneficiary Of Shifting Household Sentiment And Policy Commitment In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone Point View of Overpass and City Traffic at Night\" data-id=\"1357458696\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1357458696/image_1357458696.jpg?io=gett